      "标题": "Vul-RAG: Enhancing LLM-based Vulnerability Detection via Knowledge-level RAG",
      "作者": ["Xueying Du", "Geng Zheng", "Kaixin Wang", "Jiayi Feng", "Wentai Deng", "Mingwei Liu", "Bihuan Chen", "Xin Peng", "Tao Ma", "Yiling Lou"],
      "发表时间": "2024-06-19",
